text: Nawa may refer to: * Nawa, Rajasthan, a city and Tehsil in Nagaur district in the Indian State of Rajasthan. * Nawa District, a district in Ghazni Province, Afghanistan * Nawa, Afghanistan, a town in the central part of Nawa District, in Ghazni Province, Afghanistan. * Nawa Region, a region in Bas-Sassandra District of Ivory Coast * Nawa, Tottori, a town in Saihaku District, Tottori, Japan * Nawa, Syria, a city in Daraa Governorate, Syria * Nawa, Salamiyah, a village in the Hama Governorate, Syria * Nawa-I-Barakzayi, a village in Nawa District of Helmand Province, Afghanistan * Nawa-I-Barakzayi District, a district in Helmand Province, Afghanistan * North Africa and Western Asia * National Association of Women Artists, a US artist organisation ==See also== * Amphoe Na Wa, a district in Nakhon Phanom Province, Thailand * Maqam Nawah, a mode in the Arabic Maqam system * Nahua (disambiguation)
title: Nawa
